No. 231,

Mise.

Harrington v. California. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, William E. James, Assistant Attorney General, and James H. Kline, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

Ct. App. Cal., 2d App. Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
